                    {
                        "name": "Wolverine Rage",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The wolverine enters a state of pure rage that lasts either for 1 minute, until there are no enemies it can perceive, or until it falls <a aonid=\"38\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">unconscious</a>, whichever comes first. While raging, the wolverine has AC 17, its jaws Strike deals 1d8+7 damage, and its claw Strike deals 1d6+7 damage. While raging, the wolverine can't use actions that have the <a aonid=\"32\" game-obj=\"Traits\">concentrate</a> trait, except for <a aonid=\"84\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Seek</a>. After it's stopped raging, a wolverine can't use Wolverine Rage again for 1 minute.",
